snippet.title: Bungo Stray Dogs: Tales of the Lost - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Download now! https://got.cr/bungo-youtube

Bungo Stray Dogs: Tales of the Lost is a free-to-play mobile bubble shooter RPG, where players can attack using each character’s unique abilities to battle against villains based on the original anime. New updates and in-game content from season 2 will be available during the launch from Crunchyroll Games. The game features the original voice actors from the anime “Bungo Stray Dogs,” and exclusive storylines found only in the mobile version of the game.

Crunchyroll Collection brings you the latest clips, OPs and more from your favorite anime! Don't have time for a full episode but want to catch up on the best scenes? We've got them!

FREE 14-DAY CRUNCHYROLL TRIAL 🌟  https://got.cr/14DaysFree
